query {
  ~version:
}

docs {
  ## Get Report Template
  ดึงข้อมูลแม่แบบรายงานรายการเดียวตาม ID

  Retrieves a specific report template including its dialog (XML) and content (XML from .frx file).

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Report Template ID |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  Platform admin only — managed at Keycloak realm role level

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "name": "Purchase Request Summary",
      "description": "Summary report for purchase requests by department",
      "report_group": "Procurement",
      "dialog": "<dialog>...</dialog>",
      "content": "<report>...</report>",
      "is_standard": true,
      "is_active": true,
      "audit": {
        "created_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
        "created_by": { "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890", "name": "John Doe" },
        "updated_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
        "updated_by": { "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567891", "name": "Jane Smith" },
        "deleted_at": null,
        "deleted_by": null
      }
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 404 | Report template not found |
}
